divs: Sighting DetailsWe were driving in the car when I noticed a black, somewhat flat object thatseemed to be hovering in the sky. I had no idea what it was becuase I had never seen such an object before. At closer look I noticed that the objectseemed to rotate showing a reflective silver color on the other side. The objectwas round and saucer-like in appearance and never seemed to move except rotatingas long as I could see it. I lost sight of the object when we drove away.
